channel.description:
[size=10pt][u]RULES[/u] 1.) There will be no spamming 2.) No yelling or fighting.(Includes Cursing) 3.) No telling people there work sucks this is a constructive thread. 4.)This is not a help thread so dont ask how to do something this is just to show your future work. 5.) Lastly no advertising please I don't want your links to your models that would technically make them done so please dont post a download link of any sort.
[u]How to Post:[/u] 1.) RENDER YOUR WORK. 2.)Make it a IMAGE CODE not a link
I will try to keep the thread as active as possible please help me to do so with your work I would love to see it! Hopefully this thread will go far in showing off work that is not completely finished and will keep from making the Models thread so long. :D (MORE TO BE ADDED!)
